The package provides several fonts: Croatian Glagolitic (round-
-sometimes called Bulgarian Glagolitic, angular, Baska tablet,
cursive, ligatures, the Baromic broken ligatures,
calligraphic), Croatian Cyrillic, stecak ornaments and Croatian
wattle patterns. The fonts are provided as MetaFont source;
some Plain TeX macro support is provided, including hyphenation
patterns.
